      <title>与特朗普不同，哈里斯并不打算与中国挑起新的争端</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/harris-isn-t-looking-to-pick-new-fights-with-china-unlike-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡玛拉·哈里斯认为，美国人不希望发生全面对抗，因为他们告诉民意调查员，他们希望他们的领导人对中国采取更强硬的态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/harris-isn-t-looking-to-pick-new-fights-with-china-unlike-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 13:51:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰称俄罗斯袭击住宅区造成 4 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/ukraine-says-4-killed-by-russian-strike-on-residential-block</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰称，对一处居民区发动的袭击造成至少 4 人死亡，乌克兰总统泽连斯基再次呼吁能够使用盟友提供的武器对付俄罗斯境内的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/ukraine-says-4-killed-by-russian-strike-on-residential-block</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 13:43:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列安全内阁投票决定继续在加沙费城走廊驻军</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/israel-security-cabinet-votes-to-keep-troops-in-gaza-s-philadelphi-corridor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列政府投票决定继续在加沙所谓的“费城走廊”驻军，这一问题已成为与哈马斯停火谈判的一个关键症结。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/israel-security-cabinet-votes-to-keep-troops-in-gaza-s-philadelphi-corridor</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 13:41:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CrowdStrike 副总裁将就 IT 中断问题向国会作证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/crowdstrike-vp-set-to-testify-to-congress-on-it-outage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CrowdStrike Holdings Inc. 运营团队的一名高级成员计划出席国会，回答有关该公司 7 月份全球 IT 中断的问题，该中断扰乱了全球各个行业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/crowdstrike-vp-set-to-testify-to-congress-on-it-outage</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 13:39:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加州立法者通过法案，要求对奴隶制道歉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/california-lawmakers-pass-bill-requiring-apology-for-slavery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州立法者通过了一项法案，要求对奴隶制持续造成的危害进行正式道歉，奴隶制虽然不合法，但在 1850 年加州建州后却得到容忍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/california-lawmakers-pass-bill-requiring-apology-for-slavery</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 13:12:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉称电网“破坏”导致全国停电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/venezuela-says-sabotage-on-power-grid-led-to-nationwide-outage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉称，周五早上该国电网发生“破坏”，导致全国 24 个州“全部或部分”停电。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/venezuela-says-sabotage-on-power-grid-led-to-nationwide-outage</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 12:07:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰尚卡尔：尽管存在分歧，但印美关系“无价”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/relationship-with-us-invaluable-despite-differences-indian-fm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度外交部长苏布拉马尼亚姆·杰尚卡尔 (Subrahmanyam Jaishankar) 表示，尽管印度与美国的关系偶尔出现挫折和分歧，但印度与美国的关系仍然是最重要的关系之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/relationship-with-us-invaluable-despite-differences-indian-fm</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 11:25:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京无视战争罪逮捕令，计划访问蒙古</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/putin-defies-war-crimes-arrest-risk-with-plan-to-visit-mongolia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据两位了解克里姆林宫准备情况的人士透露，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京在访问蒙古之前得到保证，他不会因国际刑事法院的逮捕令而因涉嫌战争罪而被逮捕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/putin-defies-war-crimes-arrest-risk-with-plan-to-visit-mongolia</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 10:35:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰提议与印度举行峰会，推动结束俄罗斯战争的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/ukraine-floats-india-summit-to-push-forward-plan-to-end-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，乌克兰总统泽连斯基提议在印度举行峰会，旨在结束与俄罗斯的战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/ukraine-floats-india-summit-to-push-forward-plan-to-end-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 09:56:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
